<a class="flex-shrink-0" href="https://sofrep.com/author/wes-kennedy">
<img data-src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9986ee622c5930bd22814b2250a8767a?s=300&amp;d=mm&amp;r=r" class="object-cover w-20 h-20 rounded-full lazy" />
</a>
<div class="ml-6">
<author-desc desc="Wes Kennedy is an ex-Special Forces Operator and the Founder of Elite Training Programs, which specializes in online fitness coaching for athletes. He served for 5 years with the Canadian Special Operations Regiment and draws on his time in the SOF community as well as years of self-education and fitness coaching to provide tactical athletes with the training tools needed to arrive as physically and mentally prepared as possible on selection."></author-desc>
